# Metis Command — runtime dependencies (source of truth).
# Compile with:  pip-compile --generate-hashes --output-file=requirements.txt requirements.in
# Upgrade with:  pip-compile --upgrade --generate-hashes --output-file=requirements.txt requirements.in
#
# Version bounds below are deliberately loose to let pip-compile pick the
# highest compatible release each time we refresh.  The resulting
# `requirements.txt` pins every transitive dep with hashes.

